hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Where are you from? 365pills.net To date, the Netherlands is the most populous country to roll out a nationwide fast-charging network. Fast-chargers will be located a maximum of 50 kilometers apart along all highways, and because of ABB's multi-standard design, the network will be capable of serving EVs offered by all major car brands from Europe, Asia and the USA. ABB's open standards-based cloud connectivity solution allows Fastned to create a user-friendly payment and access service for all drivers.
